rComments: While Bruce is a great guy who tries to make lectures fun, his class is often dry & boring. That being said, the course is easy if you take good notes & have a good lab section. All of his tests & quizzes were online, even the final! Lab was worth 40% of the grade & lecture was worth 60%. Don't buy the textbook you never use it.
Great professor. Extremely knowledgeable, and detail oriented.

He is a fine teacher, tests/assignments were pretty reasonable, clear lecturer, good at answering questions, and all that.  Only problem was that I actually found the subject matter that he chose to teach rather boring.
